# Validation placement

- Implement validation **once** in `:data` (e.g. `ProjectValidation`).
- Expose field/result helpers on the feature `:api` service so presentation can show field errors.
- Presentation must **not** duplicate package/name/range rules; call the API.
- Service write paths still re-validate before mutating storage.

```kotlin
// ❌ BAD — regex / minSdk checks copied in CreateProjectScreen
// ✅ GOOD
val errors = projectService.validateCreateProject(name, packageName, minSdk)
```
